    * Backend::Store
        * BDB
        * Dir
            * Flat
            * Trie
    * DBI
        * props + blob column with Serialize role
    * SQLite
        * with dynamic alter table statements?
        * audrey style indexing?
    * Fetching
        * Scanning
        * Listing
        * Iterator
        * compat API
    * Backend::TXN
